Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&27355D\4c&27355D}{\bord3}アーリャ?　谷山?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2F4070\4c&2F4070}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2F4070\4c&2F4070}何があった?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2F4070\4c&2F4070}我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2F4070\4c&2F4070}知らないわよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&2F4070\4c&2F4070}是她汙衊我
